OL,3,CFamily's fear for autistic son as
OL,4,Ccarers' fund cut from #20 an hour to
OL,5,C#12.45
OL,7,FThe family of a young autistic man in
OL,8,FBristol say they fear for his safety
OL,9,Fand wellbeing after funding for
OL,10,Fsupport workers and therapies was
OL,11,Freduced.
OL,13,FNura Aabe's son Zak turned 25 at the
OL,14,Fend of last year, with responsibility
OL,15,Ffor his care transferring from Bristol
OL,16,FCity Council to the NHS.
OL,18,FShe said a new funding decision could
OL,19,Fhave a major impact on Zak's health.
