OL,7,F"My son has been failed by systems and
OL,8,FI continue just to just worry about
OL,9,Fthe future - it is so uncertain and I
OL,10,Fjust fear the worst is going to happen
OL,11,Fbecause last year, when my son's
OL,12,Fsupport has been stopped, he wasn't
OL,13,Feating.
OL,15,F"He wouldn't come out of his bedroom
OL,16,Fand I was just scared he was going to
OL,17,Fdie."
OL,19,FZak is described as being lively with
OL,20,Fa love of nature and the outdoors.
