OL,5,C#12.45
OL,7,FHe has intense sensory needs and type
OL,8,Fone diabetes but, with the right
OL,9,Fsupport and routine, his family
OL,10,Fbelieve he can thrive.
OL,12,FLast year the family applied for new
OL,13,Ffinancial support from continuing
OL,14,Fhealthcare funds at the NHS.
OL,16,FThe new funding deal only pays Zak's
OL,17,Fsupport workers #12.45 per hour,
OL,18,Fcompared to #20 per hour under Bristol
OL,19,FCity Council.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/7
