OL,7,FThe family fear they will lose the
OL,8,Fsupport workers who have been working
OL,9,Fwith Zak for several years.
OL,11,FNura said: "Someone with autism is
OL,12,Falways seeking some kind of clarity.
OL,13,FAnd the difficulty is we can't give
OL,14,Fhim that information because we don't
OL,15,Fknow."
OL,17,FSam Miles has been Zak's support
OL,18,Fworker for eight years and he says the
OL,19,Fsituation is heartbreaking.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/7
