OL,7,FHe said: "I can't bear the thought of
OL,8,Fjust turning around and being like,
OL,9,F'I'm sorry, mate. I've been dreading
OL,10,Fthis'.
OL,12,F"How can I talk about this without
OL,13,Fgetting upset? You get most invested
OL,14,Fwith these people when you work with
OL,15,Fthem.
OL,17,F"It's not like you just going into a
OL,18,Fshop and you're selling bits and bobs.
OL,19,FThis is another human being."
