OL,7,FA spokesperson for NHS Bristol, North
OL,8,FSomerset and South Gloucestershire
OL,9,FICB, said: "We understand the
OL,10,Fchallenges and uncertainty people face
OL,11,Fwhen they experience a change in
OL,12,Ffunding eligibility and do invite
OL,13,Findividuals and families to be
OL,14,Finvolved in as much of the assessment
OL,15,Fprocess as possible.
OL,17,F"However, in making these decisions we
OL,18,Fhave to follow a nationally set
OL,19,Fframework alongside a locally agreed
OL,20,Fpolicy for the application of
OL,21,Fcontinuing healthcare funding.
